<p>And that's it! This login step will cause the <code>currentUser</code> property to be set and
in <code>iAuthorProducts()</code> we can access that and pass it into <code>createProducts()</code> so that
each product us authored by us:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="15862f69e1">
